is those real data?

library(powstreams)
site <- 'nwis_08446500'
doobs <- load_timeseries(site, 'doobs')
aug_do <- filter(doobs, months(DateTime)=="August" & strftime(DateTime,'%Y') == '2012')
plot(aug_do, ylab = 'DO (mg/L)')

A closer look

plot(aug_do[400:750, ], type = 'o', ylab = 'DO (mg/L)', pch = 21, bg='white')
